        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Through lineage, magic, or wishes made real, the blood of a noble genie flows through your veins.</p>\n<p><strong>Spell List</strong> arcane</p>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Skills</strong> Arcana, Deception</p>\n<p><strong>Granted Spells</strong> cantrip: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Detect Magic]</em>; 1st: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Illusory Disguise]</em>; 2nd: variable (see Genie Type below); 3rd: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Enthrall]</em>; 4th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Creation]</em>; 5th: variable (see Genie Type below); 6th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Truesight]</em>; 7th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Energy Aegis]</em>; 8th: variable (see Genie Type below); 9th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Resplendent Mansion]</em></p>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Spells</strong> initial: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Genie's Veil]</em>; advanced: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Heart's Desire]</em>; greater: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Wish-Twisted Form]</em></p>\n<p><strong>Blood Magic</strong> Your spellcasting warps reality and distracts your foes. Either you gain a +1 status bonus to Deception checks for 1 round, or a target takes a -1 status penalty to Perception for 1 round.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feat-effects.Item.Effect: Genie Blood Magic (Self)], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feat-effects.Item.Effect: Genie Blood Magic (Target)]</p>\n<p><strong>Genie Type</strong></p>\n<p>At 1st level, choose the type of genie that influenced your bloodline: janni, djinni, efreeti, marid, or shaitan. You can't change your genie type later. This determines what granted spells you receive at 2nd, 5th, and 8th level.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Janni</strong> 2nd: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Create Food]</em>; 5th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Banishment]</em>; 8th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Scintillating Pattern]</em></li>\n<li><strong>Jaathoom</strong> 2nd: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Invisibility]</em>; 5th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Illusory Scene]</em>; 8th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Punishing Winds]</em></li>\n<li><strong>Ifrit</strong> 2nd: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Enlarge]</em>; 5th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Elemental Form]</em> (fire only); 8th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Quandary]</em></li>\n<li><strong>Faydhaan</strong> 2nd: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Water Walk]</em>; 5th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Control Water]</em>; 8th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Desiccate]</em></li>\n<li><strong>Jabali</strong> 2nd: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Revealing Light]</em>; 5th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Wall of Stone]</em>; 8th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Earthquake]</em></li>\n</ul>"
        },
